data.description: Home has been APPRAISED and price reduced to UNDER APPRAISED VALUE! Move in for the holidays!  Convenience of a first-floor master bedroom with a walk-in closet, dual vanity, jacuzzi tub and separate shower offers a private retreat for relaxation. The standout feature of a two-story family room, complete with a gas log fireplace adds warmth and character. For those who love to entertain, this home offers a formal dining room plus a spacious kitchen with a breakfast room & breakfast bar and a flowing open floorplan.  Hardwood floors throughout the main level and new carpet throughout the second.  Large finished bonus room has so many possibilities. Downstairs HVAC was replaced in 2023 and Roof Replaced in 2017.  Relaxing sunroom (not permitted) overlooks peaceful backyard with large brick patio. Close to downtown Fuquay and Holly Springs.
